data.description: Discover timeless charm in this 1910 Craftsman home with private detached guest house blending classic elegance with modern updates. Boasting approx. 2,023 sq feet with 1,568 sq ft. main house with an expansive living and formal dining area featuring original built-ins. The kitchen is a culinary haven with high ceilings, pot filler, and an espresso bar. The remodeled bathroom offers luxury with custom tile and heated floors.Two oversized bedrooms radiate character with hardwood floors and crown molding, bathed in natural light. Solar panels and a water softener combine sustainability. The full basement offers possibilities for a workshop, office or home gym. In addition is a detached garage with storage loft.Explore further to find a  approx 455 sq foot 1 bed, 1 bath Guest Cottage built in 2006 with a full kitchen, bathroom, inside laundry, living area, and private patio ideal for extended family . The property features a dream patio with a vegetable garden, avocado tree, fish pond, gazebo, and hot tub an outdoor oasis for entertaining or relaxation.Seize the chance to own this one-of-a-kind craftsman residence.
